---
import ArticleLayout from '../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';
---

<ArticleLayout
  title="Learn With Us | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="LEARN WITH US"
  subheading="Want to learn engineering? Look no further."
  image="/images/pages/learn-hero.jpg"
  imagePosition="center"
  description="Vehicle dynamics and aerodynamics tuition from Wavey Dynamics — bespoke courses for industry professionals, race teams, students and engineering enthusiasts."
>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">After intense years of research and learning, connecting &amp; engaging with our online community along the way and hearing your feedback, we're now offering tuition and education packages.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Whether you need 1-on-1 teaching or you're a corporate group looking to move your understanding forward. This is for you.</p>

  <h2 class="mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">What We Teach</h2>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start mb-12">
    <div class="flex-1">
      <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Initially, we're offering our experience in the following subject areas:</p>
      <ul class="wd-list space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
        <li>Vehicle Dynamics principles</li>
        <li>Aerodynamics principles</li>
        <li>Engineering Design practices</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-[240px] shrink-0">
      <img src="/images/pages/outreach-seminar.jpg" alt="Teaching session" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Who We Teach</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Our teaching material is aimed at the following audience:</p>

  <ul class="wd-list mb-12 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
    <li><strong>Corporate</strong> - into automotive &amp; motorsport</li>
    <li><strong>Industry professionals</strong>: looking to further their understanding</li>
    <li><strong>Students</strong>: studying engineering and needing some help and perhaps theory to practice at FSAE teams.</li>
    <li><strong>Educational Institutions</strong>: who look to offer material on a specific course subject</li>
    <li><strong>Race teams</strong>: looking to expand their expertise in a specific area.</li>
    <li><strong>Enthusiasts</strong>: working on projects at home, looking to build up their vehicle performance</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">How We Teach</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We're not always fans of convention — the best experience is tailored to each requirement, so here's the formats in which we provide the services:</p>

  <ol class="mb-5 space-y-3 leading-relaxed list-decimal pl-6">
    <li>Bring your problems or pain points and we'll work to get you to a solution together.</li>
    <li>Pick a specific area of interest and we'll prepare and deliver a brief course tailored to you and your learning style.</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="mb-12 leading-relaxed">Either way, you'll come away from our time with actionable knowledge and course material, to help you along the way in your future projects.</p>

  <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-10 mt-2 mb-12">
    <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Current Courses</h2>

    <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">We have recently prepared courses on the following subject areas:</p>

    <ul class="wd-list mb-6 space-y-2 leading-relaxed list-none">
      <li>
        <strong>Vehicle Dynamics Fundamentals</strong><br />
        <span class="text-sm">An A-Z of the fundamental principles of vehicle dynamics. This course runs approximately 6 hours and comprehensively covers everything you might need to know to get started as a vehicle dynamicist.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mb-6 max-w-[440px]">
      <div class="aspect-video w-full">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nG00PeG00IQ"
          class="w-full h-full"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen
          title="Vehicle Dynamics Fundamentals">
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="leading-relaxed">To read more about it and book your place, <a href="/contact" class="no-underline text-(--color-accent) hover:underline">click here</a>.</p>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest">Seminars &amp; Speaking</h2>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">It is important for us to keep up to date with the latest technologies and developments in our fields of expertise, which also allows us in a great position to contribute what we've been learning to academia and the wider industry.</p>

  <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">In recent times, we've given seminars at the MIA School of Race Engineering and to the University of Sussex on 'Suspension Design and 'Advancements in Motorsport Tyre Science'.</p>

  <div class="mb-8 max-w-[440px]">
    <img src="/images/pages/outreach-seminar.jpg" alt="Seminars &amp; Speaking" class="w-full aspect-[5/4] object-cover" />
  </div>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">For more information on past seminars, <a href="/seminars" class="no-underline text-(--color-accent) hover:underline">see here</a>.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">If you have a subject area within our expertise which you or your group would like us to come and speak on, we're here.</p>

  <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed">Check our <a href="/seminars" class="no-underline text-(--color-accent) hover:underline">courses</a> section for a little more insight into the scope of material we offer.</p>

  <p class="mb-10 leading-relaxed">Reach out and let's see what we can get arranged.</p>

  <a href="/contact" class="inline-block border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors">Get in Touch →</a>

</ArticleLayout>
